--------------------- MODULE COMMANDS ---------------------
module avail - show all available modules
module avail [module_name] - Show available modules matching module_name
module overview - Similar to module avail
module load [module_name] - Load in module_name and any dependencies (self contained)
module unload [module_name] - Unload module_name
module show [module_name] - Shows information about module (E.g. dependencies for module)
module list - Show loaded modules
module purge - Unload all modules

--------------------- LOGIN NODE COMMANDS ---------------------
uptime - Information about number of users on login node

--------------------- MISC COMMANDS ---------------------
rquota - List usage of home and scratch folders (GB used and # files)
groups - Display groups I belong to
sshare -a | grep s4736535 - Check my fair share score
--------------------- INTERACTIVE JOB ---------------------
Can change mem, time, job-name, partition (debug or general), srun as needed

salloc --nodes=1 --ntasks-per-node=1 --cpus-per-task=1 --mem=5G --job-name=MK_TEST --time=01:00:00 --partition=debug --account=a_forecasting srun --export=PATH,TERM,HOME,LANG --pty /bin/bash -l
